  - family-names: "Li"
    given-names: "Zhongyuan"
    affiliation: "AgriMind Research Group, Shanxi Agricultural University"

abstract: >
  A configurable research engineering codebase and workflow for multi-source
  agricultural breeding literature retrieval, preprocessing, relevance filtering,
  retrieval_word tagging, cleaning, deduplication, and raw inventory reporting.
  The workflow covers PubMed, arXiv, bioRxiv, medRxiv, and chemRxiv. The
  repository does not include full raw dumps, full cleaned corpora, or private
  datasets.

